title: Netflix plans expansion to 4 more Asian markets
text: Netflix plans expansion to 4 more Asian markets Wednesday, 9 September 2015 (5 minutes ago) HONG KONG (AP) â€” Netflix says it's planning to enter four more Asian markets next year as the Internet video streaming service steps up its international expansion. Netflix has ambitions to make its service available throughout the world and has already been selling its services in dozens of other countries outside the U.S.
